---
// Legacy flat bug list — superseded by /admin/tickets, which supports the
// grouping fields (component, parent_id, thesis_tag, tags) the new
// failure-bridge populates. Permanent redirect so old bookmarks and the
// API resolve/archive POST handlers (still backed by `tickets.tickets`)
// keep working transparently.
return Astro.redirect(`/admin/tickets${Astro.url.search}`, 301);
